            <lg xml:id="TK597">
<l>citaiviṭat tolkā ruravōr putaiyampiṟ </l>
<l> paṭṭuppā ṭūṉṟuṅ kaḷiṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The strong minded will not faint, even when all is lost; the elephant stands firm, even when wounded by a shower of arrows.</l>
